OL,5, A school district in the US state of   
OL,6, Utah has removed the Bible from        
OL,7, elementary and middle schools for      
OL,8, containing "vulgarity and violence".   
OL,10,FThe move follows a complaint from a    
OL,11,Fparent that the King James Bible has   
OL,12,Fmaterial unsuitable for children.      
OL,14,FUtah's Republican government passed a  
OL,15,Flaw in 2022 banning "pornographic or   
OL,16,Findecent" books from schools.          
OL,18,FMost of the books that have been banned
OL,19,Fso far pertain to topics such as sexual
OL,20,Forientation and identity.              
